flowchart LR
    U[Engineer / Researcher] --> UI[SpeechEval Web UI]
    U --> CLI[SpeechEval CLI]
    CI[GitHub Actions] --> API[FastAPI API]
    UI --> API
    CLI --> API
    API --> DB[(PostgreSQL / SQLite)]
    API --> Q[(Redis Queue)]
    API --> ST[Artifact Storage]
    Q --> W1[CPU Worker]
    Q --> W2[ASR Worker]
    Q --> W3[Optional GPU Worker]
    W1 --> V[Audio Validation]
    W1 --> AQ[Audio Quality Metrics]
    W1 --> PR[Pitch and Prosody]
    W2 --> ASR[ASR / WER / CER]
    W2 --> SP[Speaker Similarity]
    W3 --> GM[Optional GPU Metrics]
    V --> AGG[Aggregation Engine]
    AQ --> AGG
    PR --> AGG
    ASR --> AGG
    SP --> AGG
    GM --> AGG
    AGG --> INT[Benchmark Integrity Guard]
    INT --> STAT[Statistical Comparison]
    STAT --> GATE[Regression Gate Engine]
    GATE --> CARD[Benchmark Card Generator]
    CARD --> ST
    CARD --> DB
    API --> EVT[Live Run Events]
    EVT --> UI
